{{see|Pentagon}}

==English==

===Etymology===
From Greek ''pente'', '''[[five]]''', + suffix ''-gon''

===Noun===
'''pentagon''' (''plural'' '''[[pentagons]]''')
#{{geometry}} A [[polygon]] with five sides and five angles.

